@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title Source-Wire Self-Hosted Runtime Boundary

top to bottom direction

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #2F3A45
  FontColor #111827
  BackgroundColor #F9FAFB
}
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #6B7280
  FontColor #111827
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #374151
  BackgroundColor #EEF2FF
}
skinparam note {
  BorderColor #9A3412
  BackgroundColor #FFF7ED
}

actor "Memory Owner\nor Adopter" as Owner
actor "Agent Harness\nCodex / Claude / OpenClaw" as Harness

rectangle "Private Proof System\nreal data stays private" as PrivateProof
rectangle "Redaction Gate\nonly public-safe lessons move out" as RedactionGate

package "Public Source-Wire\nApache-2.0" as SW {
  rectangle "Contracts + schemas\nsynthetic fixtures\nminimal synthetic boundary" as Contracts
  rectangle "Future wrapper\nAPI + MCP policy" as Wrapper
}

rectangle "License Gate\nAGPLv3 code is audited/wrapped first\nnot copied into Apache-2.0 by default" as LicenseGate #FFF7ED

package "Separate Runtime Candidate\nSource-Wire-Memory-Engine\nAGPLv3" as Engine {
  rectangle "FastAPI + MCP\nmemory tools" as EngineApi
  rectangle "RLM search\nembeddings + rerank" as EngineAi
}

package "Owner-Hosted Environment\nBYO device / server / cloud" as OwnerEnv {
  rectangle "Owner runtime\nprocesses" as OwnerRuntime
  database "Owner Postgres\n+ pgvector" as OwnerDb
  rectangle "Owner sources\nand API keys" as OwnerInputs
}

Owner --> OwnerEnv : runs and controls
Harness --> Wrapper : calls tools through policy

PrivateProof --> RedactionGate : generalize
RedactionGate ..> Contracts : public-safe lessons only

Contracts --> Wrapper : defines behavior
Wrapper --> OwnerRuntime : future self-hosted implementation
Wrapper ..> LicenseGate : runtime fit decision
LicenseGate ..> EngineApi : audit or adapter candidate
EngineApi --> EngineAi : search + rerank
EngineAi --> OwnerDb : vector memory store

OwnerRuntime --> OwnerDb : stores owner memory
OwnerRuntime --> OwnerInputs : imports owner-approved data

note bottom of OwnerEnv
Default product path:
Source-Wire does not host other people's memory.
Each owner brings infrastructure.
end note

note bottom of PrivateProof
No private owner or client data
in public Source-Wire examples.
end note

@enduml
